{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Logo.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cursed Blood is a brutal 1-4 player co-op samurai action roguelike where players take on the role of ruthless samurai apes on a revenge spree against the mafia who exploited their sacred Shrine of Vermillion.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Shrine now demands retribution\u2014delivered by katana through swift and unrelenting violence.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner1_CoOp.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif1.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Mix both <strong>online</strong> and <strong>local co-op</strong> with friends on the couch &amp; friends joining in from across the world, all in the same run.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Or, <strong>go at it alone</strong> and see if you can get vengeance by yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner2_FastStealth.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif2.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Combine swift dashes, bullet deflection, brutal takedowns, and charged attacks to dispatch enemies with samurai-like precision. Unleash devastating finishers and heal by absorbing the blood of your foes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Carve your path through procedurally crafted levels filled with challenges, secrets, and blood filled action.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner3_PowerfulGunplay.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif3.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat enemies, seize their weapons, and turn their firepower against them\u2014until ammo runs dry. Then throw the gun back in their face and attack with a powered up katana attack to <strong>split them in half</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Blood will spray, limbs will fly and enemies will crawl away screaming for mercy, but no mercy will be given...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner4_UnlockNewKatana.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif4.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Explore a visually striking world where industrial-era machinery blends with blood-powered technology, to find ancient chests containing shards for powerful katanas and new gear.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each katana has its <strong>unique perk</strong> empowering different playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner5_UnlockNewKatana.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif5.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face a variety of increasingly challenging bosses that evolve in several stages while fighting them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat these formidable foes, grab their head and sacrifice it to the Shrine of Vermillion to bring back balance to the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner6_Replayability.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif6.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock World Mutations that drastically change the rules of gameplay and reward you with new Katanas by completing them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cursed Blood has a challenge for everyone and something to bite your teeth into for hours and hours.</p>","background":"https://store.akamai.steamstatic.com/images/storepagebackground/app/3382290?t=1739396230","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/page_bg_raw.jpg?t=1739396230","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/06bc8d3af0b86d099e97baa44c91435a40b43570/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1739396230","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/06bc8d3af0b86d099e97baa44c91435a40b43570/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1739396230","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen Co-op","id":39},{"description":"Shared/Split Screen","id":24},{"description":"Full controller support","id":28}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"Gore, swearing."},"controller_support":"full","detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https:/