s while fighting them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat these formidable foes, grab their head and sacrifice it to the Shrine of Vermillion to bring back balance to the world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/Banner6_Replayability.png?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/extras/gif6.gif?t=1739396230\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Unlock World Mutations that drastically change the rules of gameplay and reward you with new Katanas by completing them.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Cursed Blood has a challenge for everyone and something to bite your teeth into for hours and hours.</p>","developers":["David Marquardt Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Action","id":"1"},{"description":"Indie","id":"23"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3382290/header.jpg?t=1739396230","is_free":false,"linux_requirements":[],"mac_requirements":[],"movies":[{"highlight":true,"id":257087935,"mp4":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087935/movie480.mp4?t=1736980037","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087935/movie_max.mp4?t=1736980037"},"name":"Gameplay","thumbnail":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/257087935/2020485e1f5864a230d6b884c8536f616a349cf7/movie_600x337.jpg?t=1736980037","webm":{"480":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087935/movie480_vp9.webm?t=1736980037","max":"http://video.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_trailers/257087935/movie_max_vp9.webm?t=1736980037"}}],"name":"Cursed Blood","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>OS *:</strong> Windows 7+<br></li><li><strong>Processor:</st